Author: fuckwhywhywhy
Text: Society wants everyone to be stick thin and beautiful, but also wants to shove unhealthy food in your face and make you addicted to it with their added sugars so they can profit off of you  But they can’t have it both ways

Author: Pink_salts
Text: Trying to lose weight in a society that’s actively trying to keep you fat... we live in a hypocritical world.
